body:
Random GoT/ASOIF Thoughts

So, like, I’m re-reading the Game of Thrones books (A Song of Ice and Fire series) to prep for the final season of the show.

As one does when they’re obsessed.

I’m a quarter of the way through A Storm of Swords (my personal favorite) and I’m…so…bitter.

George R. R. Martin gave us a masterpiece love song, “My Featherbed” for Arya and Gendry.

Then, the show gave us an Ed Sheeran cameo in season 7. Ed Sheeran, the go-to guy for kick-ass love songs for years now.

AND THEY DON’T TAKE THAT OPPORTUNITY TO BRING GENDRY TO ARYA AND SAIL MY SHIP?!

#bitter #I will never hear this song in real life #and it hurts #it is my favorite piece of poetry/song/whatever you wanna call it #i was mad before but now I’m pissed
